  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support for a Pilot initiative to change nursing and health attention to patients and their accompaniants in three Public Health Hospitals of Managua, Nicaragua. The project aims to improve, professional and personal relations between the public and the nursing /assisstance health staff, to  improve the service and develop a co/responsibility culture in community health care,  taking advantage of a rights based approach.</narrative>
